Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:55.50,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}Faced with fresh prey, getting aroused... aroused...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.29,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}Not enough, not enough...
